# Email        : rick.romig@gmail.com | rick.romig@mymetronet.net
# Created      : 12 Dec 2019
# Updated      : 24 Oct 2025
# Comments     : For Debian, Ubuntu, Mint ... (Code from Brave's instructions)
#              : Brave is only supported on 64-bit AMD/Intel architectures (amd64/x86_64).
